{"tid":2323870,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"外賣店自願貼「安心QR」 仲係唔係黃店？","createTime":"2020-12-13T13:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T14:31:12.000Z","uid":381081,"like":16,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d5446948bc25c615019706708bdc4736089ea44","tid":2323870,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvfjsbH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvfjsbH.jpg&h=c46438e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18QrRDn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18QrRDn.jpg&h=c47364fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間喺堅尼地城嘅外賣壽司店「淞壽司」早前登記參加咗「懲罰祭」，其後有唔少商會同街坊都同我哋反映呢間「黃店」嘅立場模糊。 除咗冇張貼任何文宣（Mee Poster 都冇），連Facebook 都唔敢提及懲罰祭或相關字眼，只係輕描淡寫「11.26-29...進行優惠」。<br />\n<br />\n活動完結後，Mee團隊隨即「突擊抽查」，向壽司店負責人送出一張「SAVE12」海報，負責人拒絕即場由團隊張貼海報並承諾稍後會自行張貼。<br />\n<br />\n兩星期過去，「淞壽司」不但冇張貼過「SAVE12」海報，仲自願貼出政府用嚟監察市民行蹤嘅「安心出行QR CODE」<br />\n（根據現行法例，係冇強制外賣店貼QR CODE）<br />\n<br />\n團隊一直都諗「淞壽司」係咪有咩難言之隱，但種種跡象只係顯出：<br />\n<br />\n「佢哋唔係一間有堅定立場嘅黃店！」<br />\n<br />\n至於佢係「偽黃」、「扮黃」抑或係「藍店」就交由大家判斷，堅尼地城嘅街坊幫襯之前希望再三衡量<br />\n<br />\n最後奉勸其他「非黃店」，呢個經濟圈係歡迎大家加入，但唔好諗住賺完錢就當各位懲罰師係condom！<br />\n<br />\n『「扮黃」比藍店更￼無恥🖕🏻』<br />\n<br />\n支持我們開發App、推廣黃圈👉 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/36qF3rz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36qF3rz&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=77d02fcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36qF3rz</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n #黃色經濟圈 #支持小店 #懲罰祭 #mee<br />\nMeWe 📣  <a href=\"https://bit.ly/37DPCHb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37DPCHb&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=fde38c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37DPCHb</a><br />\nFB📱 <a href=\"https://facebook.com/PunishXi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FPunishXi&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=53ee3b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/PunishXi</a><br />\nIG 📷 <a href=\"https://instagram.com/punish_xi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpunish_xi&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=92e6ff59\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/punish_xi</a><br />\nTG 📨 <a href=\"https://t.me/punish_Xi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpunish_Xi&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=0de99e77\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/punish_Xi</a>"},{"pid":"e27d9f9cb02aa85661d055882978de15f2c9ca60","tid":2323870,"uid":60924,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怎樣才算黃店潮文召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a6f4efac93b44add0dd6d8e57aebe8b9c1b6ff","tid":2323870,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"藍扮黃 WTF"},{"pid":"30b412c0ee47d4348dd8b59bd330fe39efeb130b","tid":2323870,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"做到野"},{"pid":"6a084b1d79baae998682d66e08a52e648bfb5e7c","tid":2323870,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:04:06.000Z","msg":"樓主P牌推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6980e1d08802b832ec1e87d833accacc4a4a9491","tid":2323870,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"follow左樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d841ec5b938b66a8a499bc58e84c63ed2a13fe","tid":2323870,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:0